# Notes on orders:

- Orders cannot be merged.
- However, merged order view can be obtained by two ways
  - Grouping orders by customer
  - Order details page displays other orders of the same customer
  - When printing, offer the option to print customer orders as merged. For this to happen, a certain statuses must be matched. E.g. a completed order, archived etc cannot be included.
- Order item quantities may only be adjusted by specific role(s)
